                          CORPS Game List Server 0.3.0
                          ============================

This package contains a game list server for CORPS - The CORBA
Roleplaying System. It provides the means for game implementations
to register themselves into a publically accessible list and for client
implementation to read this list to find out about available games.

Requirements
------------

The latest version of corps-core and its dependencies.

Installing
----------

See the file INSTALL for information about compiling and installing the
package.

